    'Remove tofu and set aside; add minced garlic and ginger to the same wok and stir-fry 20 seconds until fragrant.',
    'Add sliced bell pepper and optional broccoli florets; stir-fry on high heat for 3-4 minutes until tender-crisp and lightly charred.',
    'Return the crispy tofu to the wok, drizzle soy sauce over everything, and toss on high heat for 1-2 minutes until the sauce coats the tofu and vegetables.',
    'Serve immediately while the tofu is crisp outside and the vegetables retain their crunch.',
