    'Open the cooker once pressure releases; the khichdi should look porridge-like, with rice and dal broken down into a soft, cohesive mixture.',
    'Heat 2 tbsp ghee in a small pan over medium heat; add cumin seeds and let them sizzle and darken for 30 seconds until fragrant.',
